videos.headline: Vanderbilt TE chugs in 21-yard TD snag
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur hits TE Jared Pinkney in the flat for a 21-yard Vanderbilt touchdown before halftime.

videos.headline: Missouri QB lofts 11-yard touchdown
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock lofts a screen pass to Damarea Crockett, who scoots into the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Shurmur drops in perfect fade for TD
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur floats a fade to Kalija Lipscomb, who makes an acrobatic catch for a 2-yard touchdown, giving Vanderbilt a 28-19 lead over Missouri.

videos.headline: Play-action fools defense on Missouri TD
videos.description: Missouri QB Drew Lock gets Vanderbilt to bite on a play-action call, as he slings a 20-yard touchdown to Daniel Parker, who trots in untouched.

videos.headline: Missouri survives on final play of game
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur heaves a pass on the run into the end zone but it is batted down, securing Missouri a 33-28 victory over Vanderbilt.
